data.description: HUGE price reduction! Don't miss out on this opportunity.  2 houses on 1 lot with fantastic rental potential! 5 acres with many fruit trees and scenic views. Main house has huge finished basement and attic that adds so much livable square footage. Manufactured home is a 3 bedroom, 2 bath (not included in total bedrooms) rental that is vacant and ready for your tenant. Perfect property for multi-generational family living. Property has large barn with water that's ideal for horses. Large covered parking for boat. Plenty of room for RV parking. Lots of property for vineyard planting or to continue cultivating the existing apple trees. Come see this unique property!
